text: Malax () is a municipality in Ostrobothnia, Finland. As of 31 December 2021, the municipality had a population of 5,486. Neighbouring municipalities are Korsholm, Korsnäs, Kurikka, Laihia, Närpes and Vaasa. == Other websites == * Municipality of Malax – Official website Category:Municipalities of Ostrobothnia
